"adj. 有气味的 【记】 odor(气味)+ifer(带 有)+ous→带有香味的 【例】 The rose is an odoriferous flower. adj. 有气味的 【记】odor气味, ifer带有, ous一带有味儿的 【记】odor 气味 + fer 带有，传递→传来气味的；音：熬豆，熬豆粥，发出阵阵香气 【相关】transfer 移动 odoriferous (adj.)  early 15c., ""that has a scent,"" with -ous + Latin odorifer ""spreading odor, fragrant,"" literally ""bearing odor,"" from odor (see odor) + ferre ""to bear, carry"" (see infer). Usually in a positive sense."
